creator: Bertrand Russell
description:
LibriVox recording of The Analysis of Mind by Bertrand Russell.

Read in English by Bob Neufeld; Bigcowfeet; emmablob; Kevin W. Davidson; rookieblue; Mark Johnston; David Jenkins; Ted Delorme; DPranitis; DJRickyV; and Lee Smalley.

A neat work on philosophy of mind by the 20th century analytic philosopher Bertrand Russell. (Summary by sidhu177)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
